> 
> Kernel threads?  Do this:
> 
>      strcpy(current->comm, "threadname");                       /* 16 char array!! */
>      current->mm->arg_start = current->mm->arg_end = 0;         /* black magic */
> 
> and `ps' should be happy.
Even better, use sched.c:daemonize().
